    <page class="padded-page">
        <title size="2" class="matter-text small-title">Batteries</title>
        <text class="matter-text text-block">Matter Overdrive offers 2 types of batteries. 3 if you count the creative battery.</text>
        <preview index="0" size="2" style="float:left;margin-right:7px"></preview>
        <text class="matter-text text-block" style="width:210px;margin-top:7px">The first one is the basic [item name=battery] which holds [rf name=battery].</text>
        <preview index="1" size="2" style="float:left;margin-right:7px"></preview>
        <text class="matter-text text-block" style="width:210px;margin-top:7px">Then there is the [item name=hc_battery]. It holds [rf name=hc_battery].</text>
        <preview index="2" size="2" style="float:left;margin-right:7px"></preview>
        <text class="matter-text text-block" style="width:210px;margin-top:7px">And finally there is the creative battery with unlimited FE that can only be obtained in creative mode.</text>
    </page>
</entry>
